data.description: Enjoy your privacy! Beautiful rock 1 story on tree covered acre lot!Very convenient to Austin, Home and septic pre-inspected, roof 2014, great mil floor plan with tall ceilings, gorgeous family rm w/20ft ceiling and great windows to private backyard, open kitchen with custom cabinets, 4th br or study with closet, master suite with huge walk-in closet,walk-in tub,spacious 2nd bedrooms,great utility rm w/counter space,formal dining,custom drapes and window coverings,2 car attached and 2 car detached garage! Detached garage could possibly be guest quarters, great cul-de-sac for kids to play! Many new shops and restaurants coming nearby! 5k allowance and new price 11-8!
